tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE genetic_data (
    sample_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_name VARCHAR(100),
    genetic_variant VARCHAR(250),
    test_date DATE,
    health_risk_assessment VARCHAR(200)
);

CREATE TABLE genetic_tests (
  test_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  test_name VARCHAR(100),
  test_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE health_risks (
  risk_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  risk_description VARCHAR(255),
  risk_level VARCHAR(50),
  risk_impact VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE test_results (
  result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  test_id INT,
  result_value FLOAT,
  result_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE genetic_tests (
    test_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    test_date DATE,
    test_result VARCHAR(255),
    study_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE test_results (
    result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    test_id INT,
    patient_id INT,
    result_date DATE,
    result_description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE genetic_tests (
  test_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  test_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  test_date DATE,
  patient_id INT NOT NULL,
  result TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE genetic_variants (
  variant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  variant_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  chromosome VARCHAR(5),
  position INT,
  allele VARCHAR(10)
)

CREATE TABLE health_risks (
  risk_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  risk_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  description TEXT,
  risk_factor DOUBLE PRECISION
)

CREATE TABLE patient_info (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  dob DATE,
  gender CHAR(1),
  address TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE research_studies (
  study_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  study_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE,
  researcher_name VARCHAR(255)
)
